{"tid":603664,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【大結局】《龍珠超》畫面崩壞+悟空弱智化 粉絲：鳥山明唔好再掂","createTime":"2018-03-24T03:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T13:32:15.000Z","uid":31219,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb6df1e95e82978e186966eea485a8b80e21178","tid":603664,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"自從1997年《龍珠GT》完結，相隔18年之久，龍珠迷才苦等到新一輯龍珠電視動畫《龍珠超》。經歷了2年8個月時間，日本將於3月25日播出第131集大結局，意味着橫跨了足足32年的《龍珠》電視動畫，有可能正式落幕。縱使《龍珠超》自播映以來，一直負評多於正評，但《龍珠》畢竟是風靡全球的經典神作，盛載着無數人的集體回憶，要打要鬧，粉絲們也要看完才鬧。<br />\n<br />\n好像「龍珠小站討論區」網主Joe，他於2001年《龍珠》全無新作推出的低迷時期，依然為《龍珠》建立fans網站，17年來堅持不斷更新，堪稱死忠粉絲。不過，他也對《龍珠超》甚為失望。「缺點很多，網上最多人鬧是畫面崩壞，有些畫面連小學生的畫功也不如，又經常將相同畫面重複使用。劇情亦麻麻，一些漫畫流傳下來的設定又被夾硬推翻，但我最不滿意《龍珠超》將悟空嚴重弱智化&hellip;&hellip;（下刪1,000字）」既然如此不滿，記者好奇Joe為何對《龍珠超》不離不棄，不只堅持看完全套，更對劇情背誦如流。「童年因素有一定影響，由細睇到大。當年的《龍珠》動畫真的很高質素，每星期看完一集，就很緊張想看下一集。」大概這也是不少《龍珠》迷的心聲，但Joe有感情的只限於《龍珠》作品本身，而不是原作者鳥山明。Joe更希望鳥山明不要再參與《龍珠》以後的創作，「《龍珠超》動畫證明了鳥山明已經江郎才盡。現時仍在出版的《龍珠超》漫畫，已交由《龍珠》迷漫畫家Toyble代筆，我對Toyble的信心比鳥山明大得多，希望之後鳥山明可以減少干預，讓Toyble主理。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳兆奇<br />\n攝影：伍慶泉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180324/57985822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57985822&d=2aAya40zwwW3sWBkcJntqzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=213f6fee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57985822&h=d780d5bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180324/57985822</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://dbsshk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdbsshk.com&d=2aAya40zwwW3sWBkcJntqzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=344ee9fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://dbsshk.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/dbsshk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fdbsshk&d=2aAya40zwwW3sWBkcJntqzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d3c4425e\" target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/dbsshk</a><br />\n<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"75af334ad9231817efc753ea4c64455758d648cb","tid":603664,"uid":9,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:18:45.000Z","msg":"屌 自己宣傳自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b7d95b3bc38f0059a434cbbb6666cf777effc7","tid":603664,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75af334ad9231817efc753ea4c64455758d648cb","tid":603664,"uid":9,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:18:45.000Z","msg":"屌 自己宣傳自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:23:50.000Z","msg":"殊&hellip;"},{"pid":"65f9b575640dc051e5e36ae5b55e2233712dd1d5","tid":603664,"uid":91196,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"唔係鳥山明作既龍珠邊係龍珠"},{"pid":"44ba85c88da181def972a5bb2dd833134266abaf","tid":603664,"uid":31219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65f9b575640dc051e5e36ae5b55e2233712dd1d5","tid":603664,"uid":91196,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"唔係鳥山明作既龍珠邊係龍珠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"動畫原創同劇場版大部份都唔係鳥山明作"},{"pid":"a74f7888aa8fc60b8cc5cbe4b737cefe0be88d3f","tid":603664,"uid":109809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f9b575640dc051e5e36ae5b55e2233712dd1d5","tid":603664,"uid":91196,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"唔係鳥山明作既龍珠邊係龍珠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:35:46.000Z","msg":"集英話係就係架啦"},{"pid":"0f213d6610bc435699e8203646a624e665a76772","tid":603664,"uid":54142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"其實放空腦袋去睇還是有一定價值"},{"pid":"46a